    {
      "lineNumber": 1,
      "text": "Office Memorandum • UNITED STATES GOVERNMENT",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "TO : D. M. LADD DATE: August 6, 1947",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "FROM : [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "SUBJECT: FLYING SAUCERS",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "Special Agent [REDACTED] of the Liaison Section contacted",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "Lieutenant Colonel [REDACTED] Army Air Forces Intelligence, inquiring",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "about an article which appeared in the West Coast newspapers recently",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "stating in substance that an airplane carrying recovered flying saucers",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "crashed in route from Portland, Oregon, to Los Angeles, California.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "[REDACTED] advised [REDACTED] that the only information",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "that has been received by Headquarters of the Army Air Forces is that a",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "CIC Agent of the 4th Air Forces Headquarters, Hamilton Field, San Francisco,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "was killed in an airplane crash. The Headquarters of the Air Forces have been",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "advised that he was on a top secret mission. [REDACTED] indicated that he",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "was under the impression that the CIC Agent was either on route to or from an",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "interview with [REDACTED] who is one of the individuals who first saw one of",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "the flying saucers.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "RECORDED",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "[REDACTED] stated that the Air Forces have no additional information",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "and will receive none until the report is received from the 4th Air Forces.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "[REDACTED] suggested that the San Francisco Field Office contact Colonel",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "[REDACTED] Headquarters 4th Air Forces, Hamilton Field, San Francisco, who",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "undoubtedly would be able to furnish the details regarding this matter which",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "are at this time unknown by the Headquarters of the Air Forces. [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "pointed out to [REDACTED], however, that it was his belief that no flying",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "saucers have been recovered but that it was merely an attempt to reinterview",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "an individual who previously had reported seeing one of the flying saucers.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "S[unclear]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "[unclear]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
